text: Rumors from chaos waste
Other persistent rumors have reached you: Chaos waste would also recently be surrounded by stale air. Let's hope that this is not a warning sign of something...
Chaos waste infected

Another chaotic wave was seen near the chaos waste. Unholy hordes worshiping dark gods have been summoned to the chaotic and desertic lands of the north, spreading death and desolation in their paths.
Chaos waste doomed

Terrible news comes to you from chaos waste. The chaotic and desertic lands of the north has also been invaded by chaos. Rotten from within, the earth split open and a chaotic portal opened, spewing hordes of misshapen creatures.
